{"TopicId":216273,"ForumId":139,"TopicTitle":"Patch Two On Approach","CreatedByName":"Nate Simpson","CreatedById":205123,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T18:54:00Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Nate Simpson","CreatedById":205123,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T18:54:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello fellow Kerbonauts!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOkay, we\u0027ve got a date for the v0.1.2.0 patch - it\u0027ll arrive \u003Cstrong\u003Enext Wednesday, April 12\u003C/strong\u003E. We\u0027ll post patch notes on that day as well. There\u0027s a nice blend of performance, stability, UI, and visual improvements, and we think these add up to a significantly improved KSP2 experience. One unheralded improvement, in addition to the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/215861-between-two-patches/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ealready-announced fixes\u003C/a\u003E - the nighttime lighting at \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E has taken a big step forward:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca class=\u0022ipsAttachLink ipsAttachLink_image\u0022 data-fileext=\u0022png\u0022 data-fileid=\u0022658\u0022 href=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/monthly_2023_04/image.png.5165e4c62e1a7d16c36a57cd23cfd0a9.png\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-fileid=\u0022658\u0022 data-ratio=\u002250.33\u0022 data-unique=\u0022sujticc3v\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/monthly_2023_04/image.thumb.png.809ee07300170e821627714237f29aa2.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMeanwhile, we\u0027re continuing to work on upcoming Science Mode features, re-entry and thermal systems, and of course ongoing improvements to performance and stability. We\u0027ve also begun some investigations into improving the current wobbly rocket situation, and we should have more to discuss on that subject soon.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/216289-weekly-challenge-7-land-on-eve/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EFor today\u0027s Weekly Challenge, we\u0027re going to Eve!\u003C/a\u003E Until the future arrival of re-entry heating, you\u0027ve got a great opportunity to do a little low-risk sightseeing (and if you visit after next Wednesday, you\u0027ll get to experience Eve\u0027s stunning new height fog, as well):\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca class=\u0022ipsAttachLink ipsAttachLink_image\u0022 data-fileext=\u0022png\u0022 data-fileid=\u0022659\u0022 href=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/monthly_2023_04/image.png.dafdd64dd8333462769ed4141e7efa53.png\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-fileid=\u0022659\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 data-unique=\u0022aautg5tn7\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/monthly_2023_04/image.thumb.png.fbb5d63b5332a8f499ffed19b3140ac6.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, check out this week\u0027s \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/216246-community-highlights-3/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Eburger-iffic Community Highlights post\u003C/a\u003E. So many amazing creations this week! There\u0027s also a new Tik Tok!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m heading out for a few days\u0027 rest in a place that has sunshine, which means next week\u0027s updates will be made by guest writers. Please be nice to them, but also don\u0027t be so nice to them that my bosses decide I shouldn\u0027t do the posts anymore. Please be medium nice to them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSee you in two weeks!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cheesepuffman","CreatedById":214402,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T19:04:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyippie!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tazooka","CreatedById":226666,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T19:05:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGreat to hear, I look forward to it and the patch notes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Clayel","CreatedById":223206,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T19:05:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nApril 12th, yay!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpaceExplorerW","CreatedById":217286,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T19:05:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you Nate ! I\u0027m so excited for the new patch !\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DibzNr","CreatedById":212219,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T19:06:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe sky looks wayyy nicer with atmospheric fog, always felt a bit weird having the skybox be so clear, can\u0027t wait for this update!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spicat","CreatedById":228085,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T19:09:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice, I\u0027m glad those weekly posts are staying consistent. Nice job on the fog!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Datau03","CreatedById":223270,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T19:09:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWoo!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dantheollie","CreatedById":200327,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T19:10:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI saw the art for the twitter announcement of the Eve challenge. Thought it looked a little like my Kerpernicus Eve mission badge!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooking forward to the patch notes\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0: )\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Little 908","CreatedById":228185,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T19:10:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy are the patches slowly but surely falling out of a schedule?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut thanks for the update!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FlazeTheDragon","CreatedById":226996,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T19:21:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncargo bay fix in 0.2 maybe?\u00A0( \u0361\u00B0 \u035C\u0296 \u0361\u00B0)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zeekzeek22","CreatedById":223169,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T19:23:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBest WAG guess is that last time they did thursday so they had friday to evaluate the response and implementation, and that turned out to not be enough time...so two days to bounce back this time!\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nCan\u0027t wait for that patch notes and to see what kind of performance improvement we get! One step closer!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CEO of China","CreatedById":208176,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T19:28:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwe will try to be medium nice to them\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T19:46:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224270021\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216273\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221680894630\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022228185\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Little 908\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n35 minutes ago, Little 908 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy are the patches slowly but surely falling out of a schedule?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut thanks for the update!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne patch is not a schedule.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"the_tunnel","CreatedById":227343,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T19:49:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOmg i can\u0027t wait to get it and see the performance of ksp and don\u0027t forget to get a pizza for that days lunch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Scarecrow71","CreatedById":210112,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T20:19:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224270021\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216273\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221680894630\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022228185\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Little 908\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Little 908 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy are the patches slowly but surely falling out of a schedule?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut thanks for the update!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPatches appear to be on a monthly schedule, which is fine. \u00A0But along with \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/73725-superfluous-j/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002273725\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/73725-superfluous-j/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Superfluous J\u003C/a\u003E, I gotta say that there really is no set schedule yet with only having 1 released patch and 1 on the way.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"psunavy03","CreatedById":135063,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T20:21:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224270021\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216273\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221680894630\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022228185\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Little 908\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Little 908 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy are the patches slowly but surely falling out of a schedule?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut thanks for the update!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDepends on whether the dev team is working Scrum or Kanban.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Filip Hudak","CreatedById":227970,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T20:34:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice. Looking forward to science mode when it will be developed. Finally there will be some progression mode in the game\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RE-I2 Skiff","CreatedById":223593,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T20:55:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes it count if i visit Eve in KSP1, don\u0027t have 2 yet\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T21:26:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHonestly, among usual fixes and improvements, I\u0027d very much like to see a chunk of QoL additions with every update. Even tiny things can add a lot to gameplay.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Emilius73","CreatedById":197610,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T21:41:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyay! thank you!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alexoff","CreatedById":145774,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T22:00:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow, the atmosphere scattering that was promised so long ago will be finally added to the game! Will it bring performance down to the good old 2 fps?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerbalsRus","CreatedById":196527,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T22:05:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMore parts please\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LeroyJenkins","CreatedById":227115,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T22:15:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeeee Hwwaaaaa!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022HBdwPwA.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002260.00\u0022 height=\u0022300\u0022 width=\u0022500\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/HBdwPwA.gif\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Astr0Guy5","CreatedById":225367,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T22:21:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHoorah! Less bugs, moar performance (and boosters)!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}